state.unicode: You seek to build a strong alliance with the other kingdoms of Anatolia, to act as Troy's shield against attack from without. The larger this new 'Assuwan League' grows, the harder you must fight to defend it.
Use diplomacy to create more allies and increase the effects of your alliance.

uientry.unicode: Left-click to zoom to capital, double left-click to initiate diplomacy
The number of regions this faction contributes to the Assuwan League.

state.unicode: With no allies at this point, the Assuwan League is something of an empty construct. Strike a defensive or military alliance to start building Troy's defences.
